flowchart LR
    Browser[Untrusted browser] -->|HTTPS request / WSS handshake| Ingress[Trusted ingress]
    Ingress -->|Validated Host and scheme| ASGI[Django ASGI]
    ASGI --> Controls[Session / CSRF / Origin / authorization]
    Controls --> Policy[Canonical policy and service boundary]
    Policy -->|Transactions and DB time| PG[(PostgreSQL authority)]
    Policy -->|Best-effort publish only| Redis[(Redis fan-out)]
    Browser -->|Hostile image bytes| Image[Image decode and re-encode]
    Image -->|Generated safe raster| Media[(Validated media)]
    Redis -. outage .-> Degraded[Accepted / degraded plus history resync]
    Degraded -->|Cursor fetch| Policy

    subgraph B1[Boundary B1: browser to same-origin ingress]
      Ingress
      ASGI
    end
    subgraph B2[Boundary B2: entrypoint to policy]
      Controls
      Policy
    end
    subgraph B3[Boundary B3: durable authority]
      PG
    end
    subgraph B4[Boundary B4: disposable fan-out]
      Redis
    end
    subgraph B5[Boundary B5: media processing]
      Image
      Media
    end
